        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">History</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">USSR</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->

    <section class="hero">

<video autoplay muted  loop>
    <source src="ussr.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>

        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>The Union of Soviet Socialist Republics</h1>
            <p>The Era of Joseph Stalin</p>
            <a href="#about" class="hero-btn">Explore</a>
        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- CONTENT -->

    <section class="content" id="about">

        <h2>About Joseph Stalin</h2>

        <p>
            Joseph Stalin was the leader of the Soviet Union from the
            mid-1920s until 1953. During his rule, the USSR underwent
            rapid industrialization and became one of the world's major
            military and economic powers. His leadership during World War II
            helped defeat Nazi Germany. However, his rule was also marked by
            political repression, purges, forced labor camps, and severe
            human suffering.
        </p>

